{"tid":1098544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗絕對係足球歷史上第一人","createTime":"2019-04-09T06:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T12:09:29.000Z","uid":1090,"like":9,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f92813a438fb5bed11d6ead18b1c3f68068c33d2","tid":1098544,"uid":1090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:39:12.000Z","msg":"18歲初出道曼高峰期一直keep到依家，15年時我都覺得佢差唔多收皮點知keep住有，成32歲仲可以踢到呢個地步，追平美斯金球獎（如無意外的話）。<br />\n<br />\n其實最初睇波係我覺得美斯勁好多，身為皇迷都覺佢勁，因為球技真係好撚勁，突破同個人能力絕對係當代最勁。完全唔覺c朗有咩勁叫得上球皇，但睇睇下發現c朗心態真係好強，不停咁努力追係咁操爆自己，適應力極強不單止係兩間唔同嘅球會係咁攞獎破記錄，上年仲要帶埋葡萄牙攞埋歐國杯真心痴撚線，咩年紀都仲咁有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對比美斯輸撚左就走場中離真心幫唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講美斯係勁，但佢去到30幾歲都仲可以衝擊金球，衛冕歐冠，贏埋美洲杯或世界杯，否則佢都係差c朗一皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nanyway現階段嘅球皇肯定只有c朗。睇住班盲反 搵位入，d on9 point逐個被擊破真係好心涼<br />\n<br />\n入佢響英超做山寨王，佢過皇馬更上一層樓<br />\n入佢淨係識入波刷數據，佢做埋助攻雙位數<br />\n入佢冇歐聯，呢家四年抱三跟手歷史性衛冕<br />\n入佢國家隊冇成績，佢歐國盃捧埋俾你睇<br />\n入佢淨係識弱隊屌數據，佢怒轟疤拜體祖三五七球<br />\n<br />\n個龍門仲可以搬去邊佢地先知自己有幾柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f041a27d887c89602146ee79df4d556bdefbc3","tid":1098544,"uid":18917,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:41:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4395ee43702be9bd6975568d4cac38e53e2e285b","tid":1098544,"uid":12980,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"入你老母咩 懶係有道理咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69321bf5f7a387e8c1b29cf026eecfc8f6f29a26","tid":1098544,"uid":33527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"回帶都改一改內容比d誠意啊"},{"pid":"ead0f2e05410dca0beec7826867a4ea9636150da","tid":1098544,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"好似有啲道理， 咁你分析下美斯係第幾？<br />\n會唔會超越c朗拿度"},{"pid":"9fd2fa39c94503a0b2e58019154e2e9625fb90cd","tid":1098544,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4395ee43702be9bd6975568d4cac38e53e2e285b","tid":1098544,"uid":12980,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T06:41:42.000Z","msg":"入你老母咩 懶係有道理咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758ef94b847b6b6d22bd7c7d0adae4d926599980","tid":1098544,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:07:52.000Z","msg":"唔"},{"pid":"19cfa1d4119853f9ea1592a96ed8d7a0c8db3324","tid":1098544,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"阿朗唔係唔勁，不過唔夠小花全面"}]}